C       #1432 - Pedantic handling of leading whitespace in FTP commands
C       #1475 - Minor changes to SITE command handling
C       #1486 - Directory listing performance
        #1507 - regex pattern matching in [Allow/Deny][User/Group]
C       #1564 - Add DESTDIR in Makefile
C       #1623 - "connected since" in ftpwho
C       #1644 - LogFormat local IP and FQDN tags missing
C       #1649 - setproctitle() prepends and appends process name
C       #1666 - Auth modules can return duplicate supplemental groups
C       #1682 - Broken SyslogFacility requires custom syslog code
C       #1687 - Add contrib module for RADIUS authentication, accounting
C       #1719 - Add RFC2228 stuff to distribution
C       #1736 - RETR does not handle an inappropriate REST
C       #1737 - Enhance file hiding via regular expressions

